title: CleanClean
description:
Clean Clean (officially CleanClean as one word) is the third in a series of arcade games to be released by Bus Gas Explosion Studios. In this clicker game, you are met with an endless pile of trash. Clean up as much as you can and collect hard-to-find pencils, erasers, and gumballs!

Visit their Patreon atto support the indie start-up company.
Visit http://busgasexplosion.com/ for more details and to provide feedback.
Visit https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.busgasexplosion.cleanclean for more recent updates
